Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:19.85,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Review"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:25.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akihisa and the gang found themselves suddenly{\i0}\N{\i1}participating in an inter-grade courage contest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:27.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Due to the adept strategy{\i0}\N{\i1}of the Year 3 students,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:31.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}led by the Toko-Natsu Duo, the gang{\i0}\N{\i1}found themselves in a bitter struggle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:34.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spin, spin, spin, spin, wham!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:40.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ahhh, please stop, my lord! Boom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:42.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What're we gonna do Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:44.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Many of our forces have already\Nbeen brought down by Year 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We've got a secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:48.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Se...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:49.47,Main,,0,0,0,,...cr...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:50.13,Main,,0,0,0,,...et...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:51.63,Main,,0,0,0,,...weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:01:01.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hi!! Question: Alone or together,{\i0}\N{\i1}which one is wonderful?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:20.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My future starts spinning colorfully{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:25.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How much should I tell him?{\i0}\N{\i1}Should I pretend I didn't see?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:31.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see, this vast world{\i0}\N{\i1}grows based on my mood{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:37.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you today, I really love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:42.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so stupid... My stupidity is greater{\i0}\N{\i1}than the number of the stars in the sky{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:48.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't admit my feelings for you,{\i0}\N{\i1}but I had a dream of walking with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:53.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry... It's just,{\i0}\N{\i1}I didn't know it was love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:02:00.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The answer is, you and mystery{\i0}\N{\i1}plus me equals infinite jump!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,"BAKA and TEST\N-Summon the Beasts 2-"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:24.10,Main,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.77,Main,,0,0,0,,So... he meant us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:30.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? This isn't scary at al--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay, Minami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:37.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like that. It's just that I'm\Nnot used to seeing Japanese goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,If they were German goblins, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:43.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:48.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I can't breathe... M-Minami...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:51.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh, I really can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go back, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:58.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-What is this? She isn't her usual self.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:00.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is my heart going pitter-patter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:04.10,Main,,0,0,0,,This is quite a physical trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:08.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I will eliminate the pig\Njerk who seduces my honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:09.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Run, Minami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:13.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let you get away, Honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:17.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to part you and the\Npig jerk no matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:22.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Shimizu... Right now, you look\Nmore goblin-like than an actual goblin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they came this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:34.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess we have no choice.\NLet's go check someplace else, Shimizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Honey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:41.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:44.31,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure they're really gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:47.23,Main,,0,0,0,,It's about time you get used\Nto Japanese ghosts and goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:50.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll go live in Germany then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:52.31,Main,,0,0,0,,But it'll be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:56.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I have friends in Germany, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:58.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:03:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:03.03,Main,,0,0,0,,It's us who'll be lonely if you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:04.70,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:07.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... Wh-What? You're just\Ntrying to get on my good side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true. Since we're always together,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:12.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine us suddenly being separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:14.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"Always together"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:16.92,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Minami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:21.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Then... what if I say\NI'll always be by your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Where I sit in the\Nclassroom is drafty so it's always cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.52,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not it! What I wanna ask you is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:29.02,Main,,0,0,0,,What you wanna ask me is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:33.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean... I... I... I... I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:36.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:37.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Minami? What on earth--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:43.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Akihisa. Where's Minami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:47.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I put her in bed in the nurse's office.\NLooked like she tried too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:50.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Well done, Akihisa. Our plan was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:51.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.25,Main,,0,0,0,,"Checkpoint"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:06.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Bring my honey to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:13.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Could the "secret weapon" you said be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:17.48,Main,,0,0,0,,You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:20.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? I do understand why\NShimizu is looking for Minami,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:23.53,Main,,0,0,0,,but why on earth is Kubo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:26.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! Could it be that Kubo likes Shimizu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:29.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa... you're so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:31.00,Main,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--Kubo is gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.46,Main,,0,0,0,,--What?\N--You're too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:33.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Whaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:36.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You sure did keep us waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.84,Main,,0,0,0,,We let our guard down this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:43.47,Main,,0,0,0,,but we'll now thoroughly show you\Nthe real power of the Year 3 stude--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:47.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but did\NYoshii and Shimada come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:51.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You bastard! Let me finish what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.60,Main,,0,0,0,,How dare you mock us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:54.85,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll teach you how to behave\Ntowards your upperclassmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:55.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess we have no choice... Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:59.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:04.32,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.66,Main,,0,0,0,,They've got over 400 points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:06.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.70,Main,,0,0,0,,That's science students for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:21.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Stop running around\Nso restlessly! Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:28.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.48,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Toko-Natsu Duo win"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:35.27,Main,,0,0,0,,To think that Kubo lost the battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It's about time... for us to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.40,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. You two haven't gone yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:45.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It may not be a problem for Shouko,\Nbut my physics score is 150 at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:47.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll be a very tough battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:51.45,Main,,0,0,0,,If only we had one more pair left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:53.83,Main,,0,0,0,,There {\i1}is {\i0}one more pair left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.71,Main,,0,0,0,,...right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:07:00.71,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true that I'm not\Ndisqualified since I came back,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:03.13,Main,,0,0,0,,but Minami is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:06.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! Akihisa,\Nwe've got one more person...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.80,Main,,0,0,0,,...someone who's here\Nand hasn't been disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.14,Main,,0,0,0,,One more person?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:12.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:14.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you guys talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,But she has trouble with ghosts\Nand goblins. We shouldn't push her to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll participate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:20.69,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:25.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Watching Minami,\NI thought I should try hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:29.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll enter the haunted house with Akihisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.04,Main,,0,0,0,,P-Please walk slowly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared. I'm not scared\Nat all since I'm with Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:42.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared at all.\NNot even a bit! Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:45.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:49.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for participating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm the one who's\Nalways depending on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:08:00.36,Main,,0,0,0,,No, not really. I'm even happy\Nabout you depending on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:05.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You're cute and smart...\NOn top of that, you're kindhearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:08.78,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like I'm protecting a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:13.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, the problem is, the one who's\Nwith you is someone like me who is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:16.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:19.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:22.38,Main,,0,0,0,,--What?\N--I'm clumsy and am a jealous person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:25.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I faint at critical times.\NI'm full of shortcomings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.55,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:28.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is {\i0}true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't realize it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:32.80,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't notice my shortcomings...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:39.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't it because you\Navoid getting close to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Avoid getting close to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:45.32,Main,,0,0,0,,You hold back around me\Nout of consideration for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Your eyes see me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:51.49,Main,,0,0,0,,but do you actually see the real me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:54.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa, do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:08.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot Test!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:25.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? I don't remember\Na wall being around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:31.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.62,Main,,0,0,0,,...ugly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Can it, and let go of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yuuji...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? Where is Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:43.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Hey... where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:47.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji has probably joined Shouko by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:52.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's the Toko-Natsu Duo's scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:55.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Both Shouko and\NI don't scream so easily, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.39,Main,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:10:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,So they turned off the lights\Nand separated us in the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:02.52,Main,,0,0,0,,and switched our partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:03.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:07.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, Shouko and Himeji are\Nthe strongest pair without doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:09.73,Main,,0,0,0,,So it works out okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:11.32,Main,,0,0,0,,So... what're your true feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:14.11,Main,,0,0,0,,When I'm in the haunted house\Nalone with Shouko, for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,the terror I felt when Shouko attacked\Nme with a spike rod comes flowing back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:20.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... I see Kirishima over that corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:24.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I know your true feelings really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:26.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Mizuki, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes... somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:30.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? This voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:33.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:39.81,Main,,0,0,0,,"Himeji...."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:43.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't hear anything. I can't\Nhear anyone whispering at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:46.15,Main,,0,0,0,,--Stop it. It's having the opposite effect!\N--Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:49.15,Main,,0,0,0,,If we carelessly approach them and\Nshe screams, they'll be disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:51.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Right. Let's keep a\Ndistance from them for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:56.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Tiptoe, tiptoe, tiptoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:59.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:09.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Mizuki... It's not scary. It's not scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:10.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:12.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:19.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm okay. I'm not scared.\NI'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:21.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Mizuki... Good girl. Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:27.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you might be worried, but she's\Nprobably trying her best in her own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Her best in her own way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:34.49,Main,,0,0,0,,In order to become our close\Nfriend who can be of help to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji, could what she said earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:43.33,Main,,0,0,0,,She often grumbled about\Nalways being helped by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:44.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:53.46,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Mizuki, it's not scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:59.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. I'm not scared.\NI'm not scared. I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:02.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Hang in there... Hang in there, Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.56,Main,,0,0,0,,"Last Checkpoint"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:08.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Ack! I thought you would've\Ngotten disqualified by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:11.02,Main,,0,0,0,,We've got a couple unexpected\Ninterlopers. And here we thought
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:15.15,Main,,0,0,0,,we'd get to trash those\Nscumbags Yoshii and Sakamoto first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet they hightailed it out of here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:18.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, they are scumbags, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji and Yoshii aren't scumbags.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.99,Main,,0,0,0,,They're not scumbags.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.37,Main,,0,0,0,,"They're not scumbags," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,They're always causing trouble.\NTheir grades are bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:34.59,Main,,0,0,0,,If they aren't scumbags,\Nwhat should we call them then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:37.97,Main,,0,0,0,,How about this? Instead of\Nscumbags, it's now society's trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:41.89,Main,,0,0,0,,No. That's being really rude to trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:47.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously, trash should\Nstay buried in a dumpsite!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:51.65,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. Stupid, trashy,\Nhopeless scumbags like them should be--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:54.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do you say such terrible things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:13:00.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true that Akihisa and\NSakamoto's grades may not be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:03.78,Main,,0,0,0,,They may have caused much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,But why is that alone a reason\Nfor you to say such terrible things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:08.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't know them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:12.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't know how kind they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:17.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't it really just that you\Ndon't know how stupid they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:20.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is it that you judge\Npeople based only on their grades?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:24.60,Main,,0,0,0,,There are many things that\Nyou can't measure with scores!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:28.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop shouting! Who cares\Nabout dregs like them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:35.82,Main,,0,0,0,,They are neither scumbags nor dregs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously, just shut up!\NYou're disqualified. Beat it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:43.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell us. Let's go, Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:52.29,Main,,0,0,0,,So she said, Yuuji. Apparently we're kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That's news to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:58.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Though I'm not at your level,\NI thought I was a fine scumbag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:03.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Me, too. Though I'm not at your level,\NI sort of knew that I was hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:06.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what a waste for Himeji\Nand Shouko to get disqualified like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:08.93,Main,,0,0,0,,All her effort went down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:13.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. This is just a game.\NShe didn't have to take it so seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, shall we go, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:17.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Now we're gonna get\Nserious, you damn bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Just how long are they\Ngoing to make us wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:27.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it is true that there's no way they'd\Nshow up if they saw our scores, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, upperclassmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.87,Main,,0,0,0,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:33.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get started already! Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:35.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Before that, let's decide on the penalty game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Penalty game?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:39.71,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys had better not\Nbe trying to pull something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be so alarmed. It was you guys\Nwho mentioned the penalty game first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:46.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Humph. What kind of penalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:50.10,Main,,0,0,0,,How about, the losers will do\Nwhatever the winners tell them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Ha! Fine by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's start already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:54.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.28,Main,,0,0,0,,What kind of scores are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.65,Main,,0,0,0,,They're no match for our scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:05.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Just keep running your\Nmouth. Let's go, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:08.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:09.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.99,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! They ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:12.29,Main,,0,0,0,,We're gonna go after them, Natsukawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:16.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:18.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsunemura! That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:22.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit! What a hassle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:24.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're tired already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.30,Main,,0,0,0,,The hallway over that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:28.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello there! I'm here, upperclassmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:32.31,Main,,0,0,0,,How dare he make a fool of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:34.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? You guys are slower than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:35.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I never expected them to be this slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:42.57,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way that's all they've\Ngot, is there? Right, upperclassmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:44.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii! Sakamoto! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:47.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you use those proud\Nbrains of yours and find us already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:50.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm getting tired of hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:53.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys still can't find us yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,We can see right through...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:58.29,Main,,0,0,0,,...what you guys are pulling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:15:59.25,Main,,0,0,0,,They disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:01.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Did we go out of the physics field?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:06.97,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.55,Main,,0,0,0,,We're the ones seeing through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:09.47,Main,,0,0,0,,When did they...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:11.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hasegawa!\NPlease give us approval to summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:13.47,Main,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--I approve!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:17.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm summoning my Avatar! Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:20.11,Main,,0,0,0,,We're in the math field now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:22.73,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys can't fight with your\Nfavorite subject, physics, any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What a dirty trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:28.82,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no rule against\Nswitching the subject at checkpoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Or, are you afraid of fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:32.78,Main,,0,0,0,,with subjects other than\Nphysics, upperclassmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You fools! We're good at science and math!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:38.83,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way we'll lose\Nagainst you with math, is there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:44.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.21,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:47.55,Main,,0,0,0,,That glasses guy and the rolled pigtails\Nbitch hurt our scores this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:49.01,Main,,0,0,0,,So you took that into account and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:17:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,It's too late to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:02.94,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:06.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Idiots are interesting,\Ndon't you think, upperclassmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:08.28,Main,,0,0,0,,When they become frantic about something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:10.82,Main,,0,0,0,,they exhibit an incredible\Nability to concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.99,Main,,0,0,0,,There are those who're called\Nkarate maniacs or judo maniacs, but it's
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:17.83,Main,,0,0,0,,a compliment that means "people\Nwho focus their attention on something."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,How annoying! Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.96,Main,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:26.25,Main,,0,0,0,,His head...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:32.89,Main,,0,0,0,,it means that this\Nidiot's switch got turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:34.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.01,Main,,0,0,0,,...did we...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.18,Main,,0,0,0,,...lose against these idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:41.69,Main,,0,0,0,,We won. You remember\Nthe promise, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:44.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Ha! What're you gonna make us do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:47.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:54.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Kirishima...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Mizuki is on the rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:56.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:58.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kirishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.96,Main,,0,0,0,,That's quite considerate of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Not really. I like people who try\Nhard even if they're scared, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:26.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I really like people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:30.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm neither scared of anything\Nnor do I have the will to try hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:35.74,Main,,0,0,0,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:46.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone's saying we should\Ngo have some crêpes to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:56.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Just earlier... those upperclassmen\Ncame here and apologized to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:19:00.18,Main,,0,0,0,,That's thanks to you, right, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:04.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for always causing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:06.31,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:11.32,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true that you're not a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:12.15,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,No princess would be strong enough
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:16.49,Main,,0,0,0,,to make a sharp retort\Ntowards upperclassmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:18.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... That's... uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:21.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you. It made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:24.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, Yuuji and I were\Nable to get serious and try hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you very much for saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Shall we go now?\NI think they're waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:38.01,Main,,0,0,0,,U-Uhm, there's one thing I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:39.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Something you want to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:47.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... When will you\Nstart calling me "Mizuki"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:48.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Whaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:51.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You call Minami by her first name,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,but you still haven't called\Nme by my first name all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Well, there's a complicated\Nreason that's hard to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.28,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:05.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... Well... We went to the\Nsame elementary school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:06.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:10.13,Main,,0,0,0,,So when I tried calling you by your first name,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I said "Mizuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}" out of habit,\Nand that was embarrassing, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:18.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You've never called me by my first\Nname since we started high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:21.14,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:23.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm, you won't laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:25.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Never?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:26.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:28.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm... To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:29.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:30.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, at home I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:31.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:35.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... I was practicing\Ncalling you by your first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:38.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:41.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Nothing! Nothing!\NYou didn't hear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:50.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll tell you a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.92,Main,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--To tell you the truth...
